*****How to save your maps preference for casuals*****

Select the maps you wanted to save and then save it in game. 
Then go to ...\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\common\Team Fortress 2\tf
and find the file named "casual_criteria.vdf" now right click on it and go to properties.
After that select "Read only" and save.
Now your saved maps preference will never reset.

Alternative method:

Copy that casual_criteria.vdf file to ...\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\common\Team Fortress 2\tf\custom\casualmaps
